big5_openness.HighDescription: Intellectually curious, emotionally-aware, sensitive to beauty and willing to try new things.
big5_openness.LowDescription: Preferring the plain, straightforward, and obvious over the complex, ambiguous, and subtle.

big5_conscientiousness.HighDescription: More self-disciplined, dutiful, or aiming for achievement against measures or outside expectations.
big5_conscientiousness.LowDescription: More likely to prefer the spontaneous over the planned.

big5_extraversion.HighDescription: More energetic and pronounced engagement with the external world. Likes high group visibility, talking, and asserting themselves.
big5_extraversion.LowDescription: Needs less stimulation and are more independent of their social world. It does not mean they are shy, un-friendly, or antisocial.

big5_agreeableness.HighDescription: Value getting along with others. They have a more optimistic view of human nature.
big5_agreeableness.LowDescription: Value self interests over others. They are more skeptical of others' motives.

big5_neuroticism.HighDescription: More likely to have negative emotions or get upset. It could mean they are going through a tough time.
big5_neuroticism.LowDescription: More calm and less likely to get upset. It does not mean they are positive, or happy people.

facet_intellect.HighDescription: You are open to and intrigued by new ideas and love to explore them
facet_intellect.LowDescription: You prefer dealing with the world as it is, rarely considering abstract ideas

facet_gregariousness.HighDescription: You enjoy being in the company of others
facet_gregariousness.LowDescription: You have a strong desire to have time to yourself

facet_achievement_striving.HighDescription: You have high goals for yourself and work hard to achieve them
facet_achievement_striving.LowDescription: You are content with your level of accomplishment and do not feel the need to set ambitious goals

facet_depression.HighDescription: You think quite often about the things you are unhappy about
facet_depression.LowDescription: You are generally comfortable with yourself as you are

facet_sympathy.HighDescription: You feel what others feel and are compassionate towards them
facet_sympathy.LowDescription: You think that people should generally rely more on themselves than on other people

facet_self_discipline.HighDescription: You can tackle and stick with tough tasks
facet_self_discipline.LowDescription: You have a hard time sticking with difficult tasks for a long period of time

facet_assertiveness.HighDescription: You tend to speak up and take charge of situations, and you are comfortable leading groups
facet_assertiveness.LowDescription: You prefer to listen than to talk, especially in group situations

facet_cheerfulness.HighDescription: You are a joyful person and share that joy with the world
facet_cheerfulness.LowDescription: You are generally serious and do not joke much

facet_self_efficacy.HighDescription: You feel you have the ability to succeed in the tasks you set out to do
facet_self_efficacy.LowDescription: You frequently doubt your ability to achieve your goals

facet_morality.HighDescription: You think it is wrong to take advantage of others to get ahead
facet_morality.LowDescription: You are comfortable using every trick in the book to get what you want

facet_liberalism.HighDescription: You prefer to challenge authority and traditional values to help bring about positive changes
facet_liberalism.LowDescription: You prefer following with tradition in order to maintain a sense of stability

facet_altruism.HighDescription: You feel fulfilled when helping others, and will go out of your way to do so
facet_altruism.LowDescription: You are more concerned with taking care of yourself than taking time for others

facet_self_consciousness.HighDescription: You are sensitive about what others might be thinking about you
facet_self_consciousness.LowDescription: You are hard to embarrass and are self-confident most of the time

facet_vulnerability.HighDescription: You are easily overwhelmed in stressful situations
facet_vulnerability.LowDescription: You handle unexpected events calmly and effectively

facet_trust.HighDescription: You believe the best in others and trust people easily
facet_trust.LowDescription: You are wary of other people's intentions and do not trust easily

facet_orderliness.HighDescription: You feel a strong need for structure in your life
facet_orderliness.LowDescription: You do not make a lot of time for organization in your daily life

facet_anxiety.HighDescription: You tend to worry about things that might happen
facet_anxiety.LowDescription: You tend to feel calm and self-assured

facet_friendliness.HighDescription: You make friends easily and feel comfortable around other people
facet_friendliness.LowDescription: You are a private person and don't let many people in

facet_modesty.HighDescription: You are uncomfortable being the center of attention
facet_modesty.LowDescription: You hold yourself in high regard, satisfied with who you are

facet_activity_level.HighDescription: You enjoy a fast-paced, busy schedule with many activities
facet_activity_level.LowDescription: You appreciate a relaxed pace in life

facet_cautiousness.HighDescription: You carefully think through decisions before making them
facet_cautiousness.LowDescription: You would rather take action immediately than spend time deliberating making a decision

facet_dutifulness.HighDescription: You take rules and obligations seriously, even when they're inconvenient
facet_dutifulness.LowDescription: You do what you want, disregarding rules and obligations

facet_artistic_interests.HighDescription: You enjoy beauty and seek out creative experiences
facet_artistic_interests.LowDescription: You are less concerned with artistic or creative activities than most people who participated in our surveys

facet_immoderation.HighDescription: You feel your desires strongly and are easily tempted by them
facet_immoderation.LowDescription: You have control over your desires, which are not particularly intense

facet_emotionality.HighDescription: You are aware of your feelings and how to express them
facet_emotionality.LowDescription: You do not frequently think about or openly express your emotions

facet_adventurousness.HighDescription: You are eager to experience new things
facet_adventurousness.LowDescription: You enjoy familiar routines and prefer not to deviate from them

facet_anger.HighDescription: You have a fiery temper, especially when things do not go your way
facet_anger.LowDescription: It takes a lot to get you angry

facet_excitement_seeking.HighDescription: You are excited by taking risks and feel bored without lots of action going on
facet_excitement_seeking.LowDescription: You prefer activities that are quiet, calm, and safe

facet_cooperation.HighDescription: You are easy to please and try to avoid confrontation
facet_cooperation.LowDescription: You do not shy away from contradicting others
